  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to know the distribution of HP in stomach before use of PPI,
      during use of PPI, and after stop of PPI.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Endoscopy and biopsy will be performed to investigate the distrubition of HP before, during,
      and after using PPI.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
